_sText:
This is a trap map,the first in its category,this game style was developed by me,Tom [IrNinja]
It is not based on any deathrun map because i did not know of deathrun untill this map was finished,so leave the critisism about that out plz.
I would want to wish u alot of funs and good luck reaching the end;)

NOTE: This map has got Terrorist spawns only ,to respawn while playing => hit "M" Choose terrorist and a T-character,after entering u will just respawn.(respawn mod might be a good idea)

NOTE2:This map is best suited for Fun-Servers


NOTE3:For more efficient use of the map type in console the following two commands:
           Mp_Autoteambalance 0
           mp_autokick 0
